  "original_title": "\u0d9a\u0ddd\u0da7\u0dd2 24 \u0d9a\u0ddc\u0d9a\u0dda\u0db1\u0dca \u0dc3\u0db8\u0d9c \u0db4\u0ddd\u0dbd\u0db1\u0dca\u0dad \u0da2\u0dcf\u0dad\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0dba\u0dcf \u0db8\u0dcf\u0da7\u0dca\u0da7\u0dd4",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Polish man caught with 24 crores of cocaine",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mr. Sudatta Silva, Customs Media Spokesman, Deputy Director of Customs (Legal Affairs) said that a Polish national has been arrested with a cocaine drug stock with a street value of 24 crores and 50 lakh rupees.",
        "He had come from Colombia to Doha, Qatar and from there he had arrived at Katunayake Airport by Qatar Airways flight.",
        "But because he could not find the suitcase he had brought at that time, when he came back to Katunayake Airport to take the suitcase, the officials of the Customs Drug Control Division, who were suspicious about the suitcase, found a used fax machine inside. In several rolls of paper, this cocaine drug stock weighing 05 kg was found while being hidden.",
        "At present, after arresting this stock of drugs and the Polish national who illegally brought them to Sri Lanka, the officers of the Customs Narcotics Control Division have handed them over to the officers of the Police Narcotics Division for further investigations."
      ],
